  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>PizzaExpress</strong> <strong>pizza dough</strong> in half</p><p>Shape the<strong> dough </strong>into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> balls and set aside for 15 min</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1666198613825-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1666198613825-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1666198613825-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1666198613825-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1666198613825-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dice the<strong> mozzarella </strong>into small bite-sized pieces and add to some kitchen paper</p><p>Press down on the <strong>diced mozzarella</strong> with another piece of kitchen paper to squeeze out as much liquid as you can</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-copy-1666198618261-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-copy-1666198618261-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-copy-1666198618261-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-copy-1666198618261-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1-copy-1666198618261-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your<strong> garlic oil</strong></p><p>Slice the<strong> portobello mushrooms</strong></p><p>Strip the <strong>rosemary leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1666198623475-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1666198623475-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1666198623475-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1666198623475-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1666198623475-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the dough balls have rested for 15 min, press your palm into the middle of a <strong>dough ball</strong> to flatten it until it is twice as wide</p><p>Turn the<strong> dough </strong>over and repeat a few times, until approx. 24cm in diameter (use a<strong> rolling pin</strong> to help you!)</p><p>Repeat with the other <strong>dough ball<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>– these are your <strong>pizza bases</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>pizza bases</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or 2!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1666198629761-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1666198629761-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1666198629761-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1666198629761-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1666198629761-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread 2 tbsp <strong>finely chopped tomatoes</strong> over each pizza base (save the rest for another recipe!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong>, <strong>diced mozzarella </strong>and<strong> chopped rosemary</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>garlic oil</strong> and season with a double pinch of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1666198636192-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1666198636192-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1666198636192-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1666198636192-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1666198636192-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray in the oven and cook for 9-19 min or until the pizza bases are golden and crisp and the mozzarella has melted</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? You may have to do this in batches!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-1666198640172-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-1666198640172-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-1666198640172-x700.jpg",
