          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-1666198640172-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel the <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> until you end up with a pile of cheese shavings – this is your <strong>shaved cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-copy-1666198644035-x200.jpg",
