    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pizzas are ready, top them with the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>shaved cheese</strong> – these are your <strong>funghi di bosco pizzas</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>funghi di bosco pizza</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
